<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= pageTitle || "Alt App" %></title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600&family=Pacifico&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        /* Inline styles for quick adjustment */
        .content-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header-container">
        <div class="header-title">
            <%= headerTitle || "Welcome!" %>
        </div>
        <div class="nav">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a href="/register">Register</a>
            <a href="/stats">Reports</a>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section style="max-width: 700px; margin: 2rem auto; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>
            Welcome to our application! This project was built to make managing users and
            data simpler, faster, and more reliable. Our team is passionate about creating
            easy-to-use tools that help people stay productive.
            </p>

            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
            We aim to deliver clear, efficient solutions that save you time. Whether it’s
            handling registrations, keeping your information secure, or streamlining your
            workflow — we’ve got you covered.
            </p>

            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <p>
            Have questions or feedback? Reach out at
            <a href="mailto:support@example.com">support@example.com</a>.
            </p>
        </section>
        
    </main>
    <footer>
        Built by <%= author || "Default Admin" %>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
